    <knowl>
        <content>
            <list>
            <item><p>Sketch a graph of the function <m>y = \tan(x)</m> on the domain
            <m>[-\pi,\pi]</m>. Include any <m>x</m>- or <m>y</m>-intercepts and 
            any horizontal or vertical asymptotes on your sketch.</p></item>
            <item><p>Sketch a graph of the function <m>y = \arctan(x)</m>. 
            Include any <m>x</m>- or <m>y</m>-intercepts and 
            any horizontal or vertical asymptotes on your sketch.</p></item>
            </list>
        </content>
        <outtro>
            <list>
            <item><p><image 
                source = "assets/PGTA/generated/{{__seed__}}/Show1.png"
                description = "the graph of $y=\tan(x)$"
            /></p></item>
            <item><p><image 
                source = "assets/PGTA/generated/{{__seed__}}/Show2.png"
                description = "the graph of $y=\arctan(x)$"
            /></p></item>
            </list>
        </outtro>
    </knowl>
